title: Week 2 Studs & Duds + Monday Punday, Turd Alert! - Fantasy Football Podcast for 9/19
description:
Week 2 reactions! On today’s fantasy football podcast, Andy, Mike, and Jason review the studs and duds from the Week 2 action! Which players are worth hitting the Panic Alarm on? Who will bounce back in Week 3? Plus, big injury updates and Monday Punday! Manage your redraft, keeper, and dynasty fantasy football teams with the #1 fantasy football podcast. -- Fantasy Football Podcast for September 19th, 2022.
